{"tid":1556831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找如何持續大叫的正確方法！","createTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:32:04.000Z","uid":319799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f8d3decd1fc61faf85fa38126add488adcfefe","tid":1556831,"uid":319799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:12.000Z","msg":"每晚十點，各位巴絲想必一定對住個窗口放聲嚎叫。小弟係住慈雲山，晚晚都叫足9個字，但依幾晚明顯少左手足回應，回應到既都已經把聲沙哂或拆左，而我自己把聲都唔多掂，唔知有冇巴絲可以提供有效嘅發聲方法出黎，廣傳開去，等各區巴絲嗌得舒服啲、持久啲。同時一問有冇邊隻喉糖、喉嚨藥好推介，因為依加係連正常講野都喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！"},{"pid":"6c0f51496d06e578d073da58cec5d09ea4dbe9fa","tid":1556831,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"喇叭？"},{"pid":"c49b3aa55bc3ea8af6059bdec33b15a11905fa12","tid":1556831,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:36:53.000Z","msg":"播香港國歌"},{"pid":"cc9fcbbf5a675f139c61abc17149d879991848fb","tid":1556831,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"唔識點形容 原理就好似丹田咁（夠響夠大聲但唔痛，但好似冇丹田呢樣嘢） 唔好夾硬扯把聲（聲會沙會走音會feel到痛）<br />\n或者去youtube睇下有冇教學"},{"pid":"c3cc8761393afd3c2efc8fe3f6d98f62c4875612","tid":1556831,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"比人拉晒 所以愈黎愈少人應"},{"pid":"d22888e1f5287b7a2b75127d1abc83278d91b1af","tid":1556831,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"用單田"},{"pid":"3d52062bd614f3fd090afcc963eba4303f622cc3","tid":1556831,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"用丹田唔好用喉嚨呀"}]}